      "path": "/books/kitab-al-mumin:4:6",
      "source_url": "https://thaqalayn.net/hadith/30/1/4/6",
      "text": [
        ": قال النبي (ص) المُسلمُ أخو المسلمِ لا يخونُه ولا يخذِلُه ولا يعيبُه ولا يحرمُه ولا يغتابُه."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.muhajir-b-ali": [
          "98. It has been reported that Abu 'Abd Allah (a.s) said: The Prophet (a.s) said: A Muslim is a brother to the other Muslim; he must not betray him, desert him, disgrace him, excommunicate him nor backbite him."
        ]
      }
    },
